thread.title: Amanda Chetty

author: Amanda Chetty
title: Amanda Chetty
text: From the moment I logged onto FreeLogoServices I have had excellent service. Signing up is as simple as can be. After sign-up service is brilliant. The company is extremely customer focused with an acute understanding of what small businesses need. I would recommend them to anyone without hesitation. There is a time difference of approximately 8 hours between the country I live in and where FreeLogoServices are based - even the time difference makes NO difference. They are efficient and effective.
